Developer Terms of Use
des:
With this Alexa Skill, SPINE Magazine will list for you anticipated new books appearing on bookshelves every week!

SPINE Magazine covers creative and production aspects of the book publishing industry. Its mission is to offer creator insight, long-form stories, product information, and community content for an audience that is highly enthusiastic about books.
